{"type": "article", "id": 42162, "title": "宜家教你做饭：填好空，一道菜就做好了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-06-19T22:58:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 8451, "name": "李奥贝纳"}, {"id": 41601, "name": "Magenta"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 204, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170619220037F95SDb8RpzLavIqt.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Cook This Page by Leo Burnett &amp; IKEA</h3><p>如果你买过宜家的家具，一定不会对那些图示清晰的组装图感到陌生。最近，宜家加拿大就在当地的广告公司<a href=\"http://www.leoburnett.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\">李奥贝纳</a>的帮助下，推出了一套采用相同风格设计的食谱 Cook This Page。秉持着再手残也能做好一道菜的宗旨，打印在烘培用羊皮纸上的食谱更是将一切从简发挥到了极致：只要将列出的材料根据图示比例放在纸上，再将羊皮纸卷起后放入烤箱就能做好一道菜了。不过，作为宜家加拿大的营销，这些看起来像是完形填空的食谱暂时没有对外销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220121ChlQAfzdcU4m6Ft0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220122U2zAfFB0uqyPiJS7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220122qCeMX6QWGk1yw0S5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220122dztSLG6gWjJhfM1X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220124LuSEOHlNRi5VPABJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.538667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MICRO by Kickstart Success</h3><p>转换插头一直都是出国旅行的必备品之一，但多合一的模块化插头往往会因为体积大增加行李负担。最近，来自英国的设计团队 <a href=\"https://kickstartsuccess.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kickstart Success</a> 开发了一款号称史上最小的转换插头 MICRO，6*3.1*1.8 厘米的大小可以轻松地塞进衣服口袋里。和需要将不同模块组合在一起的插座不同，MICRO 的插头和可拆卸的外接组件全部集合进了适配器内，能够在不同插头间灵活转换。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1249002224/micro-the-worlds-smallest-universal-travel-adapter\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 23 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220139l3gxmTabypBz5MHD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220139w9NtQIr2SAk6a3Xi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.373529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220139wPTUNSWzpi1VYuna.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220140uf4zQcUb7lxMWSon.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706192201418y3uTPQ01Y2aVNXB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jupiter &amp; Juno by Giselle Jonte</h3><p>西班牙设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gisellejonte\" rel=\"nofollow\">Giselle Jonte</a> 以罗马神话中神明 Jupiter 和妻子 Juno 的形象为灵感，根据以他们命名的天体运行轨迹，构思了一款同名的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/52850201/Jupiter-Juno-watch\" rel=\"nofollow\">腕表</a>。没有刻度的表面由磨砂金属制成，代表时针和分针的两根轨迹围绕着正中央代表太阳的圆点旋转，时而接近时而远离，充满了简约的美感。目前它处于概念设计阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220236us7m2txYPRTOQkIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220236bpmZeqVglJEWvokT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220236lgAPXrh5um4kDwzR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706192202377QVyLIJZqXbA6lD8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706192202374Eq60PQIzF2NZk5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>8 TICKETS by MANÎ Diseño estratégico</h3><p>为了吸引年轻的消费者，很多公司都在尝试打造新的形象，西班牙设计工作室 <a href=\"http://maniestudio.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MANÎ Diseño estratégico</a> 则从体验入手，带来了一款与游戏结合的葡萄酒包装 8 TICKETS。酒瓶的标签上印有一张虚构的地铁线路图，上面的路线都是以适合来上一杯的场合命名的：无论是生日派对还是下班后的夜晚，你都可以在路线中被特意加粗的 Wine 站放松自己。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220257RPyNXE4lDtU7ehki.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220257dX9B5qh3eF8HvVGT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220256zNoZwG1ebyPnC5vI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220258MglFSCsRDT7otcpu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Opposite by Magenta</h3><p>你有没有好奇过用乐高积木的反面搭建模型会是什么样？在今年的<a href=\"https://www.jdw.co.il/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">耶路撒冷设计周</a>上，设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.magentaworkshop.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Magenta</a> 带来了一系列名为 Opposite 的金属组件，利用上面的小孔，人们可以颠覆传统，将乐高积木反过来安装在一起，由此开发出丰富的组装方式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706192204117d3Ph9NTHmeSqaov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.506112\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220409TfblSL8Fj5C74Bda.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732274\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706192204103ehKvrCgXURiyou5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220409RZtTuesEmO3G7Mfk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Paper Sculptures by Gunjan Aylawadi</h3><p>现居悉尼的印度裔电脑工程师 <a href=\"http://www.gunjanaylawadi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gunjan Aylawadi</a> 以用纸条替代织线打造的编织作品见长。在过去的几年中，她以在家乡常见的几何图形、建筑风格和阿拉伯图案为灵感，将细长的纸条扭曲、彼此交错，打造了一系列有着优雅弧度的小型纸雕。目前，她的作品展 <a href=\"http://www.gunjanaylawadi.com/place-for-prayer-1/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Place for Prayer</a> 正在悉尼的 <a href=\"https://www.koskela.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Koskela 画廊</a>正在举行，将持续至 6 月 24 日。你还可以在她的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gunjanay/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 上看到更多作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220324vShrMobU0yEackAw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220325MngwfPyzpcYrSsDG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220325SPzy38EOKgMrDR6Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.949000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170619220326BDlQorjcOvEn1dte.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.349000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}